WEBVTT

00:02.816 --> 00:04.297
The day is too short.

00:05.865 --> 00:12.086
That's why at night, Torin Yater-Wallace keeps skiing in an ocean of snow.

00:13.790 --> 00:15.226
It's only him out there.

00:16.981 --> 00:18.765
Wild and free.

00:21.999 --> 00:24.240
I'm Torin, this is my everywhere.

00:24.665 --> 00:27.892
Supporting Olympic athletes for over 25 years.

00:28.285 --> 00:30.608
VISA, everywhere you want to be.

